title: Dynamite★Beauty
original_name: ダイナマイト・ビューティー!!
sinopse:
A local high school is thrown into chaos when Wakaba Sakurada, a gorgeous 21-year-old teacher-in-training, joins the faculty. Wakaba goes to incredible lengths in her attempt to become the best art teacher she can be, including modelling nude for her students!

(Source: Animaxis)
